Additionally, their successful completion of the TREASURE RELAY TOUR [REBOOT] reinforced their reputation as versatile all-around artists. In 2025, they are set to connect with fans worldwide through a global fan concert tour.

After making a powerful statement with their 2024 digital single ‘KING KONG’ and showcasing their multifaceted charm with ‘LAST NIGHT’, TREASURE is now returning with their SPECIAL MINI ALBUM ‘PLEASURE’. He was instrumental in developing the BU assessment tools, rating system, and instructional resources. Dr. Dave is also a long-time monthly instructional columnist for Billiards Digest magazine and an active participant in online billiards forums and social media. He is a devoted authority and an expert in understanding and teaching the physics of the game. description:
I caught my first fish, a bluegill, at the age of 5 using a cane pole and bobber in my grandfather's pond in SE Nebraska.  Growing up in Colorado, my dad and I frequently fished for trout in our local rivers and the beaver ponds near the mine where he worked.  At the age of 17, an older friend took me fly fishing for the first time.  We fished Tenmile creek, near Copper Mountain, and I still remember catching my first fish on a dry...a size 14 royal wulff.  Needless to say I was hooked.

Since then, my fly fishing adventures have taken me all across the western United States including guiding in both Alaska and Oregon, chasing steelhead in British Columbia, fly casting competitions, and pursuing bonefish, tarpon and permit in Belize. 

Fly fishing has been a major passion in my life now for over 30 years and I’m excited to now bring some of my adventures to you.

FFH

My videos are meant for entertainment purposes only and are in no way instructional.  Do not attempt yourself.

He is the only golf instructor to have designed his own research software, Jacobs 3D, which measures the forces and torques at work in a golf swing. He is the author of three books—The Elements of the Swing, Swing Tips You Should Forget, and his latest release, The Science of the Swing.

What's the goal of Mostly Pizza? Well - there are plenty of videos on YouTube around how to make pizza, from the dough, to the sauce, to ensuring you have that perfect crust. However, none of them seem to compile them in a way to make it easy to follow, and the videos that are great are sparse throughout the YouTube universe - so you have to hunt for what you want to find. Here, you'll be able to find all things (mostly) about Pizza, from making your own ingredients, preparing the dough, making the sauce, ensuring you have the right tools and of course, making the pizza. Let's take the nervousness out of it, and make some of the best pizza you've ever had.

Disclaimer: I'm not a chef, I have no training (obviously), and have only been making various pizzas for the past 4 years. While I continue my journey around learning how to make pizza, I'm going to record it now and share with everyone.

Slow Motion is the name given to the slow motion effect, widely used in cinema to create tension or amplify moments of climax. In addition, it is also used as a language and cinematographic tool by super cameras capable of recording images that our eyes cannot capture.

🕒 Slow motion can also be used for artistic effect, to create a romantic or suspenseful aura or to stress a moment in time.

Welcome to our channel. We are the Fisher Family and we would love for you to join our family of 8 as we learn priceless life skills as we start homesteading on our 1/2 acre yard.

We hope to encourage you to give homesteading a try and experience the many blessings that can come from the life of a homesteader. We will share both our successes, as well as, our failures. We have fit chickens, dairy goats, a small family garden, and  6 kids on our homestead. We are passionate about nutrient dense traditional food and believe that because our food system is broken. We believe that everything we have has been given to us by God and that we are to be good stewards of this life.

Join us in our homesteading journey as we patiently await our dream to minister to others with a larger farm. Until then, we will "Turn our waiting room into a classroom." (Jessica Sowards, Roots and Refuge)

description:
昆虫は世界中で約100万種が確認され、地球上で最も繁栄した生物と言われています。しかし、日常生活では意外に目にする機会は少ないもの。これは、昆虫があまりに微細で動作も速いため、人間のスケール感では捉えきれないためです。さらに、視覚や聴覚も人間の感覚を遥かに超えた世界に生きているため、ますます理解不能な存在となっています。目立たずひっそり暮らしたい昆虫たちにとっては好都合なことかも知れません。
最新の映像技術を用いると昆虫たちの興味深い世界が見えてきます。マクロレンズで拡大し4Kの高精細動画で撮影した動画は新しい発見の連続です。1秒間に1000～5000コマ撮影できる高速度カメラでもたくさん撮影しています。チョウやトンボ、甲虫などの多種多様な飛翔スタイルや、カマキリやハンミョウなど肉食昆虫の目にもとまらぬハンティング、セミやコオロギ、キリギリスなど鳴く虫たちの発音の秘密など、「身近な隣人」昆虫たちの知られざる世界に迫ります。昆虫観察は、動画を繰り返し再生して観察することを強くおすすめします。

description:
Oficjalny kanał You Tube wytwórni muzycznej HYPSTERIA RECORDS
Hypsteria założona w 2019 przez grono entuzjastów muzyki i mody. Spontanicznie, odważnie i przemyślanie z pomysłem na siebie. Tworzymy muzę taką jak lubimy łącząc style muzyczne. Odkrywamy „podziemie” polskiej muzyki alternatywnej i hip-hop, czerpiemy z najlepszych źródeł muzycznych. Oryginalność i osobowość jest naszą dewizą na rynku muzycznym. Z obowiązujących trendów czerpiemy wybiórczo.
Prowadzimy kariery młodych i zdolnych artystów wybierając i doradzając im w ich ścieżce muzycznej przy tym kolaborując z najlepszymi studiami i producentami muzycznymi w kraju.  
Współpracujemy z najlepszymi…
Lubimy gadżety. Czerpiemy z inspiracji „młodych zdolnych” nie do końca jeszcze odkrytych przez main stream.
Nie jesteśmy tylko wytwórnią, squadem, grupą ziomali czy agencją artystyczną. Jesteśmy przede wszystkim towarzystwem artystycznym otwartym na każdego, kto myśli twórczo i chce się realizować. Zapraszamy do do współpracy z nami!

description:
When I was a young boy (1950's), I learned to play golf by closely watching the best players at the course I grew up on. I would then stand in front of a window and copy their swings... then I would go to the practice area to ingrain that look and new feeling to muscle memory. That WAS and STILL IS a great way to learn! It's called SELF-DISCOVERY! 

When you discover a helpful motion or thought ALL BY YOURSELF, YOU WILL NEVER FORGET IT! - I never have!  

At the age of 78, I'm still a mid single-digit player. My goal with this YouTube channel is to provide a platform for TEACHING and LEARNING! I will provide videos and detailed descriptions of the finest golfers in the world, their swings and some of their finest shots so YOU can learn and improve as I have. 

The focus here is geared toward TEACHING and LEARNING the short game (putting, chipping, pitching and wedge play from 120-yards in), but you will also see some of the finest, Tour-Proven full swings and descriptions as well.⛳️

description: Too many people assume that gradual erosion and decay of the body over time is an inevitable part of life. Given the percentage of people suffering from chronic pain in the joints, you could not be faulted for believing they are right. The truth is, this assumption is wrong. Physical degeneration of the joints is not inevitable, You can choose to keep your joints healthy and functioning over a long lifetime if you choose to become conscious of how to move your body correctly. How you function, when you walk, stand, sit, or do any of your normal daily activities, determines whether or not your joints will stay healthy over the long haul. I believe that knowledge and practice are the keys to proper function and maintenance of healthy joints. You don't need a pill. The best time to learn how to move consciously and correctly is before you start having pain, but I believe that it is never too late. The information is here. The future is in your hands.

Woof woof,

My name is Lucifur The Pug. I sleep, I play and I be myself 🐶

If you like my videos please like, subscribe and share.

For those who think my name is evil please read the actual meaning of name Lucifer.

"Lucifer" is the rendering of the Hebrew word הֵילֵל‎ (transliteration: hêylêl; pronunciation: hay-lale) in Isaiah (Isaiah 14:12) given in the King James Version of the Bible. The translators of this version took the word from the Latin Vulgate,which translated הֵילֵל by the Latin word lucifer (uncapitalized),meaning "the morning star, the planet Venus", or, as an adjective, "light-bringing".

As a name for the planet in its morning aspect, "Lucifer" (Light-Bringer) is a proper name and is capitalized in English. In Greco-Roman civilization, it was often personified and considered a godand in some versions considered a son of Aurora (the Dawn).A similar name used by the Roman poet Catullus for the planet in its evening aspect is "Noctifer" (Night-Bringer).

description:
Welcome!  
This channel is all about being more in love with nature, along with life lessons and fun. 

This channel showcases chipmunks, black squirrels, raccoons, red squirrels, chickadees, deer, blackbirds, wild turkeys, ducks, Canada geese, and any other interesting wildlife we come across during our nature walks.  

I started this Channel to help people smile more during the pandemic.   I just took my phone out on my nature walks, and shared my experiences with wildlife. 

The basic values of this channel are:
1.  Encouraging people to be more in love with nature. 
2.  Promoting a sincere effort towards humility:  I like to remind myself that the Universe is infinite and so is my ignorance. 
3.  Inspire people to be more loving to all beings, because when we love greatly - we live greatly. 
4.  Keep things fun:  As Yogananda says, we're here for 2 reasons:  Our education and entertainment!

What does ‘GOAT’ mean?

“Greatest of All Time”
GOAT stands for “greatest of all time.” If you’ve participated in online sports talk, you may recognize that the term is used to refer to the greatest athlete in the history of a professional sport. Alternatively, some use it to refer to the best currently active athlete in the field. Because of its prominence, it has also become a general term for an all-time great at topics outside of sports.

Some examples of athletes who have been referred to as the GOAT of their respective sports include Tom Brady, Muhammad Ali, Serena Williams, Michael Phelps, and Tiger Woods or maybe Leo Messi, Novak Djokovic...

Thanks so much for everything, I love playing Sport  with an appetite for love, laughter, destruction and drama,  prepare yourself for anything and everything to enjoy your own life

description:
Imagine what the world would look like if you can stretch a 1 second action in 40 seconds.  To do so require specialized cameras that can shoot a minimum of 1000 frames per second.  Yes, 1000 photographs in a single second.    These photographs are stitched together to create super slow motion video.  

To watch such 1 second events in slow motion expands your mind and I assure you - it will relieve stress as well.  So please slow down with me and watch the videos in its fullest.  

While you will see that the natural world dominates the videos, there will be studio shots as well.  

Please watch with audio and in large screen for enhanced viewing experience.
Please DM me for any related business opportunities.
Massachusetts, USA.

description:
Tumble Doctor, LLC conducts world-class tumbling camps, clinics, and classes for cheerleaders, gymnasts, and coaches.
-----------------
There is a huge difference between how gymnasts are trained and how cheerleaders are trained. Gymnasts are trained to perfect every skill prior to progressing to the next skill. Cheerleaders tend to be trained to progress as quickly as possible even if that means skipping (or simply not mastering) fundamental skills. Such training grants gymnasts the ability and confidence to learn new skills the correct way while minimizing fear and injuries. 

Now, we are all humans. We are all subjected to the constraints of gravity, friction, air resistance, tension, etc. These are all constants dictating the way we live and the way we tumble. And thus, only the internal forces are relative; the, proverbial, inner drive is what distinguishes a good athlete from a great one. It is my fervent mission to create confident, technically sound athletes.

Can I Use PianoNest tracks for my cover videos on YouTube?
Absolutely! We love to see PianoNest's tracks being used on YouTube! However, PianoNest only own the copyright of the Sound Recording, but not the Composition of the song. In most cases, the owner of the Composition (songwriters/ authors/publishers) love when people are making covers of their song. But they also have the rights to claim and monetize your video, or even (these rarely happens): remove your video, and/or causing a strike to your channel.
PianoNest tracks are managed by RHEI Music (VISO). You may receive a claim notification when using PianoNest tracks. This is normal and this doesn't mean you’re in trouble and will NOT negatively affect your account standing, it’s just our claim of ownership.
Please note, that by using PianoNest tracks you may NOT:
- Upload cover video to YouTube’s Content ID
- Upload video of the track by itself with no creative addition
- Monetize your video
- Create lyrics video karaoke

Light a candle, put on your headphones, and allow GHOSTE to happily haunt your ears. Bold and cinematic, GHOSTE manifests songs both inspirational and introspective; a gem of multilayered emotion brimming with melancholy, passion, imagery, longing, and self-confidence." (IndiePulse). Soul-soothing vocals summon alto shades of Annie Lennox with undertones of an edgier Sarah McLachlan dressed in evocative soundscapes created by multi-instrumentalist and producer Matt Anthony (Tammany Hall NYC).

Diving fearlessly into the more nuanced emotions of the human psyche, GHOSTE alluringly transforms struggle into shining hope, faithful to her favorite expression, per aspera ad astra (through struggle to the stars).

BTW, the E is silent. GHOSTE is not. 👻

For fans of Annie Lennox, Sarah McLachlan, Enya, Sonia Stein, Lorde, Maggie Rogers
